    <h3>Purpose</h3>
    <p>PLOS ONE is conducting a randomized controlled trial of manuscripts to gather data on how the reporting of published in vivo animal studies is impacted by the inclusion of the ARRIVE checklist.  Editorial Office will assist with two phases: </p>
    <ol>
        <li>Identifying appropriate manuscripts for inclusion and requesting the checklist </li>
        <li>Recording compliance in the randomization engine website</li>

    </ol>

    <p class="red">PLEASE NOTE: it is critical that you do not tell authors that we are conducting a trial because this may change their behaviour and responses.</p>
